  "description": "Justin-Ames Gamache®, M.Ed., M.S., is a scholar-practitioner and doctoral candidate in Educational Technology at the University of Phoenix. He holds graduate degrees in education and psychology, along with interdisciplinary undergraduate study. His public academic and scholarly work engages higher education, educational technology, mindfulness, identity, student well-being, qualitative research, and inclusive learning environments.",
